The Deadman's chest is a cosmetic platebody that can be bought from Justine's stuff for the Last Shopper Standing for 160 Last Man Standing points. It is part of the Deadman armour set.

In Deadman Mode, it has the stats of an iron platebody and is purchased from Nigel for one blood money, and may be reclaimed for free. In order to purchase deadman armour in Deadman mode, players must use the blood money on Nigel, instead of speaking to him, as there are no dialogue options for purchasing the armour.
